# This directory holds bundled Hunspell `.bdic` spellcheck dictionaries.
#
# Populate it before building with:
#   yarn dictionaries:download
#
# The desktop main process points Chromium's spellchecker at this directory via
# a file:// URL (see app/javascripts/Main/Window.ts ->
# configureSpellCheckerDictionarySource) so dictionaries are served locally
# instead of being fetched from Standard Notes' host. The webpack CopyPlugin
# copies this directory into app/dist/dictionaries at build time.
#
# `.bdic` files are gitignored (see .gitignore); only this placeholder is
# tracked so the directory exists in a fresh checkout.
